Class StateHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • StateHolder

  • public class StateHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    This object can hold a QWOPGame's state at a snapshot. It can then compare itself to another state and return some metric of how close the two of them are.
    Author:
    Matt
